@Node Intro "Introduction"

 Introduction
 ============
 FreeFreq is a program that allows you to generate file requests (*.REQ 
 files) with a comfortable GUI. FreeFreq is font-sensitive and resizable
 and is designed to work especially well together with TrapDispatcher, a
 scheduler for TrapDoor that I also have programmed.

@EndNode

